            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Yeees?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Excuse me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Fritz. Are you here to see Plachta?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "No, not today. I've come with some information for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Information...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yes... About those twins."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Twins... Do you mean Meklet and Atomina?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Indeed. I saw those two at a certain place, and figured I should tell you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "So you saw them, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Right, you said that Oskar spotted them before. At the \"Sealed Temple\"..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "This time, I saw them in the \"Fallen Palace\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "The Fallen Palace... Sophie, what should we do?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, it might be pointless again... But we should probably check."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Fritz, thank you for the information. We'll try going to the \"Fallen Palace\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I see, you should let me know when you decide to go. I'll see you then."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Oskar, and now Fritz... Considering they both witnessed the same thing, it must not be a mistake."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... I hope we can find them this time..."
        }
    ]
}